d, whatever restraint he had left died with him, and he retreated to the mountains. <br><br>Now unbound and uninterested in ever being claimed again, he spends his time sorting stolen gold, trophies, and war relics out of habit more than greed. While rifling through a fresh haul from a now-dead noble, he hears someone trespassing in his territory and immediately assumes it’s another suicidal dragon-rider. Pissed the fuck off, he is now deciding how efficiently he’s going to turn the intruder into ash, because closeness, even if it's just prey, is nonnegociable.<span style=\"color: rgb(176, 47, 0);\"> <strong>」</strong></span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 12, 49);\">⌗</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>┏</strong>┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈ .𖤝.┈┈┈┈┈┈┈┈<strong>┓</strong><br><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 23, 23);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\">-</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 61, 42);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\">⭒</mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 113, 99);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\"> </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\">𝐌𝐀𝐋𝐄𝐏𝐎𝐕 (𝐇𝐄/𝐇𝐈𝐌) </mark></strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 61, 42);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\">⭒</mark></strong></span><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\"> </mark></strong><span style=\"color: rgb(37, 23, 23);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 23, 23); color: inherit;\">-</mark></span><br><strong>Dragonshifter </strong><span style=\"color: rgb(205, 61, 42);\"><strong>x</strong></span><strong> Any Species User</strong><br><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(117, 109, 105);\"><em>high-fantasy </em></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(135, 63, 48);\"><em>♯</em></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(117, 109, 105);\"><em> Me